{"id":9600,"date":"2025-11-26T12:56:28","date_gmt":"2025-11-26T12:56:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=9600"},"modified":"2025-11-27T11:01:26","modified_gmt":"2025-11-27T11:01:26","slug":"bali-3","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/bali-3\/","title":{"rendered":"BALI"},"content":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[109],"activities":[],"trip_types":[127],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[125],"class_list":["post-9600","trip","type-trip","status-publish","hentry","destination-romantic-indonesia","trip_types-honeymoon-international-tour","tripcategory-honeymoon-international-tour"],"packages_ids":[9602],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-9600","price":85000,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":7,"nights":6,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"","cost_includes":"Return Economy Airfare BOM-BOM\nAccommodation mention or similar hotel. \nBreakfast, Lunch, Dinner \nMeet & Greet assistance at the airport and transfer directly to your hotel, Day at leisure \nReturn Airport& Inter Hotel Transfer by Pvt Basis. \nEnglish speaking driver cum guide assistance. \nTraditional welcome garland on arrival \nPer Person 1x 500 ml Water bottle during tours & transfers \nTravel  goodies","cost_excludes":"Any meals other than those mentioned above included. \nVisa charges \nGST 5% \nAny portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all Items of personal nature. \nAny services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions. \nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle mal- Functions, political disturbances etc.","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What is the best time to visit Bali?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best time to visit is during the <strong>dry season (April to October)<\/strong> when the weather is sunny and ideal for beaches and sightseeing.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. Do I need a visa to visit Bali?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many nationalities get <strong>Visa on Arrival (VoA)<\/strong> or <strong>visa-free entry<\/strong> for short stays. Always check updated travel requirements before your trip.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. What are the must-visit places in Bali?","content":"<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Ubud<\/strong> (rice terraces, temples, culture)<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Uluwatu<\/strong> (cliff views, temple, beaches)<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Kuta &amp; Seminyak<\/strong> (nightlife, beaches)<\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Nusa Penida<\/strong><\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Tanah Lot Temple<\/strong><\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Tegallalang Rice Terrace<\/strong><\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Mount Batur<\/strong><\/li>\n<!-- \/wp:list-item --><\/ul>\n<!-- \/wp:list -->"},{"title":"4. Is Bali safe for tourists?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, Bali is generally safe. Just stay cautious with traffic, beach currents, and personal belongings in crowded areas.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"5. What is the local currency in Bali?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The currency is the <strong>Indonesian Rupiah (IDR)<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/trip\/9600","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/trip"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/trip"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9600"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/trip\/9600\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9601,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/trip\/9600\/revisions\/9601"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9600"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"destination","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/destination?post=9600"},{"taxonomy":"activities","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/activities?post=9600"},{"taxonomy":"trip_types","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/trip_types?post=9600"},{"taxonomy":"difficulty","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/difficulty?post=9600"},{"taxonomy":"trip_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/trip_tag?post=9600"},{"taxonomy":"tripcategory","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory?post=9600"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"http